text: Femke Bol (; born on 23 February 2000) is a Dutch athlete."Femke Bol", World Athletics. Retrieved 8 June 2024. She has run 400 metres in 49.17 seconds and 400 metres with hurdles in 51.45 seconds. She won a bronze medal at the Summer Olympics in 2021 and two gold medals at the World Athletics Championships in 2023. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Medalists at the 2020 Summer Olympics Category:Dutch hurdlers Category:Dutch sprinters Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Olympic bronze medalists
